		<hr size="1">Brusco's has a 0 duration stun effect when it hits.  It doesn't do much damage but it does interrupt casting pretty consistantly.  The Brusco's you get later on has an 8 second stun and does a base 222 damage but the recast time on it makes it a little annoying... of course that 8 seconds allows for a full tick's worth of dots to work on your target... combine that with the 222 and you're looking at around 800 damage in those two ticks, not too shabby.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
